    • withJavaPath

      public UpdaterOptions.UpdaterOptionsBuilder withJavaPath(String javaPath)
      Set the path to the java executable to use with Forge and Fabric installers. (Directly the java executable, not the java home) If you wish to set up the java home, you should use the System.setProperty(String, String) method with the "java.home" key. By default, it's taken from System.getProperty("java.home").
      Parameters:
      javaPath - the path to the java executable.
      Returns:
      the builder.
